{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setMetaMarshal","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"marshalData"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gpointer"},{"text":"? = nil, ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"metaMarshal"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:gclosure.h@T@GClosureMarshal","text":"GClosureMarshal","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"! = nil)","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A meta marshaller wraps the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"closure"},{"type":"text","text":"’s marshal and modifies the way"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"it is called in some fashion. The most common use of this facility"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"is for C callbacks."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The same marshallers (generated by ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"#glib-genmarshal","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"are used everywhere, but the way that we get the callback function","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"differs. In most cases we want to use the ","type":"text"},{"code":"closure","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"’s callback, but in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"other cases we want to use some different technique to retrieve the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"callback function.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For example, class closures for signals (see","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_type_cclosure_new()"},{"text":") retrieve the callback function from a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"fixed offset in the class structure.  The meta marshaller retrieves"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the right callback and passes it to the marshaller as the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"marshalData","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" argument."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glibobject\/closureprotocol\/setmetamarshal(marshaldata:metamarshal:)"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ClosureProtocol\/setMetaMarshal(marshalData:metaMarshal:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"s:10GLibObject15ClosureProtocolPAAE14setMetaMarshal11marshalData04metaG0ySvSg_ySpySo9_GClosureVGSg_SpySo7_GValueVGSgs6UInt32VSPyAMGSgA2GtXCSgtF","role":"symbol","title":"setMetaMarshal(marshalData:metaMarshal:)","extendedModule":"GLibObject","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setMetaMarshal"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"marshalData","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gpointer","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer"},{"kind":"text","text":"?, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"metaMarshal"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:gclosure.h@T@GClosureMarshal","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GClosureMarshal"},{"kind":"text","text":"!)"}],"modules":[{"name":"GLibObject"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the meta marshaller of "},{"code":"closure","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ClosureProtocol"]]},"reference